.SH "NOTES"
.PP
The attributes max_recv_wr and max_recv_sge are ignored by
.B ibv_create_qp()
if the QP is to be associated with an SRQ.
.PP
.B ibv_destroy_qp()
fails if the QP is attached to a multicast group.
